			"a_h2": "Built From This",
			"a_description": "The distinctive visual aesthetic of Typographic-First — a design approach that creates unique, memorable interfaces. Background: light (#ffffff). The .inner panel has a clean background with subtle border treatment and appropriate border-radius. Colors: #222222 as the primary accent for interactive elements and highlights. #111111 for headings, #777777 for body text. The aesthetic captures the essence of typographic-first through careful color choices, spacing, and visual weight. Set in EB Garamond — chosen for its visual character that complements this design style. Heading at weight 600-700, 24-28px, line-height 1.2-1.3. Eyebrow at weight 500, 11px, uppercase, 2-3px letter-spacing, color #222222. Body at weight 400, 14-15px, line-height 1.6-1.7, color #777777. Buttons: primary — #222222 background with contrasting text. Secondary: transparent with #222222 border. Alternatives: system-ui (universal fallback), serif stack.",
